Setup & Installation

pre-requisites: 
1.Docker(it needs permission to run/access) which I have already done
2.Kind(kubernetes in Docker)
3.Kubectl
4.Helm (you can install ArgoCD using Helm or cube kubectl)
⭐️Helm is used in Production(recommended)

create KIND-Config file(vim KIND-Config.yaml)- this is a manifest file
(This create's a kind cluster)

